@JennyMaden Hello Jenny,
we have answered through DM.
Thank you.

@Aeroslavee @shewalkinglikea Hola Román,
para verificar la situación, le pedimos que nos indique el número de su caso y la dirección de correo electrónico asociada.
Para salvaguardar la confidencialidad de sus datos, le sugerimos que los envíe por mensaje privado. Gracias.

@mauriciorfls Olá Maurício,
desde já, pedimos desculpa pelo tempo de espera.
Pelo seu número de processo de bagagem perdida, localizámos o processo de reclamação. O mesmo ainda está em análise e será contactado com a maior brevidade possível. (1/2)

@TalesLisboa2 Hello Tales,
we have answered through DM.
Thank you.

@rodvalladares @TAP_AIRLINE Hello Rodrigo,
if we can still help you through this channel, please provide us with your booking reference. For confidentiality reasons, we suggest you to send the details by private message. 
Thank you.

@edelahozuah Hola Enrique,
hemos respondido a su mensaje privado.
Gracias.

@LuucyCope Hello Lucy,
We express our sincere condolences to your family,
May you please let us know the booking code or ticket numbers via DM, so we may assist you?

@zineb17_ Hello Zineb,
May you please let us know your complaint number or ticket numbers via DM, so we may assist you?
Thank you.

@Regina_deHeer Hello Regina,
We sincerely apologize for the inconveniences caused by the irregularity on your luggage transportation.
May you please let us know if you have filed any complaint and which is its number via DM?

@DebLFR Hello Debby,

can you inform us through DM the following details:

- booking reference or electroni ticket number (047...),
- what are the contents of the bag;
- does it require to be in a freezer? ;
- does the passenger tranport any needle and how many?

Thank you.

@pmnbarbosa Olá Pedro,
para que possamos verificar, pedimos que nos confirme o número de caso e o endereço de e-mail associado ao mesmo. Por motivos de confidencialidade, sugerimos o envio dos dados por DM.
Obrigado.

@MrNunoCarvalho Olá Nuno,
respondemos por mensagem privada.
Obrigado ✈️

@wallycantsee Hello lkdtap@gmail.com, 
to verify, please confirm us your booking reference or ticket number and your TSA KTN. For security reasons, we suggest sending the details by DM.
Thank you ✈️

@joseadlcr Hola José,
hemos respondido a través de DM.
Gracias.

@Zach41091718 Hello Zach,
Please provide us with the reference number and e-mail address that was associated with the claim, so we may verify.
Thank you.

@jeremyatl1 Regarding the upgrade, Jeremy, we suggest checking the TAP Miles&amp;Go Terms and Conditions - https://t.co/LPI7iVQmiN
For further information, please contact TAP Miles&amp;Go Assistance Center - https://t.co/ftyXSzQwrg
Thank you.

@Vuper678 @UK_CAA Hi R,
we have replied by DM.
Thank you.

@carolc1965 Hello Carol,
we are verifying the situation. As soon as we have further information, we will let you know right away.
Thank you ✈️

@dominikjaeger Hello Dominik,
We are deeply sorry that your situation hasn't been handled yet. We have reinforced your case and you will be contacted per e-mail as soon as the analysis of your situation is completed.
Thank you.

@dannicerqueira @staralliance Olá Daniele,
apresentamos as nossas sinceras desculpas por qualquer inconveniente ou transtorno causado. Se pudermos ajudar com alguma questão e/ou de alguma forma por esta via, estamos ao dispor.
Obrigado.

@jeremyatl1 Hello Jeremy,
we are truly sorry for any misunderstanding or inconvenience experienced. Please allow us to inform however even if the fare itself does not have a rebooking fee associated, if applicable, fare difference is chargeable.
Thank you.
